fields.name: 8kg Kettlebell
fields.description: From a glance, this is a traditional 8kg kettlebell. But it is not. This kettlebell has the new great feature of having a soft feel despite the fact it is still heavy, solid, and very good balanced. This is the perfect kettlebell for home use when it will be a friend to floors and feet.
